name: Backyard Wrestling 2: There Goes the Neighborhood
name_original: Backyard Wrestling 2: There Goes the Neighborhood
description:
Backyard Wrestling 2: There Goes the Neighborhood is an arcade-fighting game developed by Paradox Development Studio. It came out on 16-11-2004. Eidos Interactive published the game.
Backyard Wrestling 2: There Goes the Neighborhood is available on PlayStation 2 and Xbox.
